narration_text: #C C holds a plate.
#C C rolls the dough.
#C C picks a tortilla rolling machine.
#C C removes polythene from the machine.
#C C pulls her cloth.
#C C puts the dough on the machine.
#C C removes dough from the polythene.
#C C fixes the tortilla on the machine.
#C C puts the dough on the mat.
#C C removes the polythene.
#C C puts the tortilla on the machine.
#C C closes the machine.
#C C rubs on the tin
#C C opens the tin
#C C picks the polythene paper from the tin
#C C places the polythene paper with sticker on the cloth
#C C removes the polythene from the sticker
#C C spreads the polythene paper on a sticker tin
#C C closes the tin
#C C rubs on the tin
#C C opens the tin
#C C picks the polythene paper from the tin
#C C places the polythene paper with sticker on the cloth
#C C removes the polythene from the sticker
#C C picks the polythene papers
#C C raises the hands
